    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "It should henceforth be the life study of both husband and wife how to avoid everything that creates contention and to keep unbroken the marriage vows.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"5T 122.1\" data-link=\"113.612\"> Testimonies for the Church 5:122</span>.</span></a></sup>",
